559
00:33:04,120 --> 00:33:05,120
"Forever Enemies"

560
00:33:05,380 --> 00:33:07,590
<i>Jika Kak Sa Ra menerimaku kembali, dia bisa apa?</i>

561
00:33:07,590 --> 00:33:09,120
<i>Dia sudah merencanakan ini.</i>

562
00:33:09,120 --> 00:33:11,090
<i>Dia bilang ingin mengembalikan semuanya.</i>

563
00:33:11,090 --> 00:33:12,519
<i>Apa kita butuh gugatan?</i>

564
00:33:12,519 --> 00:33:14,160
<i>Sakit! Tolong!</i>

565
00:33:14,160 --> 00:33:15,759
<i>Kamu tahu dia siapa?</i>

566
00:33:15,759 --> 00:33:17,499
<i>Bibimu bersikap aneh.</i>

567
00:33:17,499 --> 00:33:19,259
<i>Jangan dekati keluargaku.</i>

568
00:33:19,259 --> 00:33:20,569
<i>Mereka seperti pasangan.</i>

569
00:33:20,569 --> 00:33:21,969
<i>Apa mereka berkencan?</i>

570
00:33:21,969 --> 00:33:23,799
<i>Lama kelamaan rindu bisa memudar.</i>

571
00:33:23,799 --> 00:33:25,200
<i>Itu Ha Ji Na.</i>

572
00:33:25,200 --> 00:33:26,969
<i>Bibi mencoba segala cara untuk bisa kembali.</i>

573
00:33:26,969 --> 00:33:28,370
<i>Kemarilah sekarang! Cepat!</i>

574
00:33:28,370 --> 00:33:30,380
<i>Aku akhirnya datang.</i>

